create a product
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/products -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"title": "Product1", "description": "Description of Product1", "price": 100}'

get all products
curl http://localhost:3000/products

get single product
curl http://localhost:3000/products/<product_id>

update a product
curl -X PUT http://localhost:3000/products/<product_id> -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"title": "Updated Product", "description": "Updated Description", "price": 150}'

delete a product
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/<product_id>
